{
  "stem": "13096.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You see, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] because they were the only people-- not only that, they were sending-- you know, they had our names.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Every month, you know, they were sending, individually, to each one, a parcel of clothing, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So much so that we had too much, because we were poor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And you know what poor it is, because the many poor in Italy at the time after the war, you know, they were just going from place to place, from house to house, to collect the charity.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were so sorry for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Sometimes, you know, when we had enough of our clothing, we would make a little parcel at night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we'll throw-- And the house of the rabbi was on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We will throw through the window, you know, a parcel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Whoever found it, found it, the surplus that we didn't need it, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because one poor, you know, understand the other poor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Like you see, you know, in the films, some beggars, you know, they got a piece of bread, they share it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But when you are rich and you have too much, you don't like to share to other people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After Bologna, you know, my brothers that they were in Africa, they heard that we were there, that they are also trying to send money, and the help, and whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, you know, they send-- and they make, you know, the arrangement for us to go to the Belgian Congo, where they live themselves.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it took, you know, to make all this paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you have to have, you know, like somebody to sponsor you to come to Belgian Congo at the time, like in South Africa and all this.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
